{"tid":1072333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賴清德：不必另外宣布台灣獨立","createTime":"2019-03-22T03:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T10:01:32.000Z","uid":109462,"like":202,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"7df9308bf2cf4a1d228cbd170082a08567dcde69","tid":1072333,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"提務實台獨3方向 賴清德：不必另外宣布台灣獨立<br />\n2019年3月21日 下午8:24<br />\n<br />\n前行政院長賴清德登記民進黨初選，挑戰總統蔡英文。賴清德今晚於臉書po文表示，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「台獨」，台灣已獨立的簡稱</span></strong>，不必用一句話，兩個字就可以說清楚了，就是「台主」，「台」灣自己當家作「主」，捍衛「台」灣民「主」的意思。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/L_tNteK7ssUvbS1XTveLRg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/3ce8ff66440bb6b9d7bf2f9e32be72d7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FL_tNteK7ssUvbS1XTveLRg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F3ce8ff66440bb6b9d7bf2f9e32be72d7&h=db7083b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔡總統今天赴民進黨中央登記總統初選，她說「民進黨需要我，台灣也需要我」，她願意再次承擔下一個階段責任；擔任台灣總統必須有3個條件，「這3條件的答案就是蔡英文」。<br />\n<br />\n賴清德晚間說，他是個務實台獨工作者，他的務實反應在三個方向：<br />\n<br />\n1、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">台灣已經是個主權獨立的國家，名字叫中華民國，與中國互不隸屬，不必另外宣布台灣獨立。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2、台灣前途由兩千三百萬人民決定，任何人都不能，那怕是總統，其他任何人都不能干預。<br />\n<br />\n3、台灣當前最重要的工作就是發展經濟、建設國家、造福人民，壯大台灣。<br />\n<br />\n賴清德也表示，國家的前途，由台灣人民自己決定，「呷飯皇帝大」顧好百姓、發展經濟，是他一貫的主張，從未改變，相信也是多數台灣人民的共識。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8F%90%E5%8B%99%E5%AF%A6%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A83%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91-%E8%B3%B4%E6%B8%85%E5%BE%B7%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%85%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-122425845.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%258D%25A83%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2590%2591-%25E8%25B3%25B4%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25BE%25B7%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%2585%25E5%258F%25A6%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B-122425845.html&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroEx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=074bc27c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8F%90%E5%8B%99%E5%AF%A6%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A83%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91-%E8%B3%B4%E6%B8%85%E5%BE%B7%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%85%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-122425845.html</a>"},{"pid":"46d6001b8cc80a88e54fa8076e99d00f6baa0269","tid":1072333,"uid":136431,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:07:25.000Z","msg":"佢呢隻係華獨嚟"},{"pid":"2f8ae1c5d5022a8aa404f64f1b97a5d38f0e878d","tid":1072333,"uid":109462,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"照佢咁講即係台獨運動已經完滿成功，各個台獨政團同組織都可以就地解散返屋企瞓覺，往後不必再提「台獨」二字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9191c6f5771d201d3948b042cefd46d26ea5700e","tid":1072333,"uid":87339,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"2f8ae1c5d5022a8aa404f64f1b97a5d38f0e878d","tid":1072333,"uid":109462,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"照佢咁講即係台獨運動已經完滿成功，各個台獨政團同組織都可以就地解散返屋企瞓覺，往後不必再提「台獨」二字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:08:51.000Z","msg":"民進黨發現再打統獨已經攞唔到著數<br />\n<br />\n比韓國瑜打殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e35d92e6ecbc679e44215de3bed323004072e2","tid":1072333,"uid":166474,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"任何地方都有權宣佈獨立，問題係有幾多國家承認你，冇國家可以自成一國，完全冇盟友支持，唔解決中共孤立你每日宣佈一次台灣獨立都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcba2b2f5013fea11ef6a8c5aa0ef0d765c42ff","tid":1072333,"uid":87515,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"港主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d23b70d9f8fff0127640114cf09f8681eca211","tid":1072333,"uid":132038,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:12:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b2e127da202e5aea85f224593139f4944e96860","tid":1072333,"uid":136431,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2f8ae1c5d5022a8aa404f64f1b97a5d38f0e878d","tid":1072333,"uid":109462,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"照佢咁講即係台獨運動已經完滿成功，各個台獨政團同組織都可以就地解散返屋企瞓覺，往後不必再提「台獨」二字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:14:39.000Z","msg":"口吻好似香港堆泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賴清德啲台獨立場好撚飄忽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951e48bd6e93801dcd66469c23d9161ce29d12a0","tid":1072333,"uid":109462,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9191c6f5771d201d3948b042cefd46d26ea5700e","tid":1072333,"uid":87339,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"2f8ae1c5d5022a8aa404f64f1b97a5d38f0e878d","tid":1072333,"uid":109462,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"照佢咁講即係台獨運動已經完滿成功，各個台獨政團同組織都可以就地解散返屋企瞓覺，往後不必再提「台獨」二字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:08:51.000Z","msg":"民進黨發現再打統獨已經攞唔到著數<br />\n<br />\n比韓國瑜打殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:18:12.000Z","msg":"林右昌訪美 提新路線新主張：成為全世界華人的民進黨<br />\n2019-03-10 09:12<br />\n<br />\n〔記者俞肇福／基隆報導〕基隆市長林右昌帶領的訪美團，美國時間9日抵達紐約，首站前往紐約台灣會館，對上百名台僑發表公開演說，獲得熱烈歡迎；同時，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林右昌也以民進黨前代理主席身分，提出未來的民進黨不能只是台灣的民進黨，而是應做為世界華人的民進黨</span></strong>，首度針對民進黨的未來新路線提出主張。<br />\n<br />\n他也向現場的台僑說，面對選舉失利時大家不要氣餒也不要喪志，未來的民進黨應連結世界上與民進黨有相同價值的人來擴大力量、一起支持台灣；另外，也要加強海外的力量，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民進黨要從本土的、台灣的民進黨蛻變成華人的民進黨。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2722048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2722048&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroEx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=04c0d74a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2722048&h=2c9b1837\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2722048</a><br />\n<br />\n全部人一齊向中華民國靠攏，變到「華頭華腦」；估唔到過咗幾十年之後都係要玩返兩蔣嗰套，要台灣做返全球華人嘅自由燈塔、民主長城<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de873fd5c91603daaad401f3bb0fb0c6e4e16347","tid":1072333,"uid":208722,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"華獨當臺獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貴國福建省點呀又"},{"pid":"cf07c37e329ff9e4bcd7233a5923a501586dfcf2","tid":1072333,"uid":49388,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"1、台灣已經是個主權獨立的國家，名字叫中華民國，與中國互不隸屬，不必另外宣布台灣獨立。<br />\n<br />\n民進黨唔係主張建立台灣共和國咩<br />\n瀨咁既主張同國民黨有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7fce884d2f8b18b3721126a8286672376e1db0","tid":1072333,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b2e127da202e5aea85f224593139f4944e96860","tid":1072333,"uid":136431,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2f8ae1c5d5022a8aa404f64f1b97a5d38f0e878d","tid":1072333,"uid":109462,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"照佢咁講即係台獨運動已經完滿成功，各個台獨政團同組織都可以就地解散返屋企瞓覺，往後不必再提「台獨」二字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:14:39.000Z","msg":"口吻好似香港堆泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賴清德啲台獨立場好撚飄忽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"務實台獨工作者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190e4d31994d78ef3fc969df3844560ef2d33178","tid":1072333,"uid":65604,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"依種走精面獨立係最蠢，你唔正式宣佈獨立，將中華民國條根徹徹底底斬去，將來民粹一轉，後患無窮。"},{"pid":"e44244e65ee15a9dc05b3b915985e0ea2f8e9ed1","tid":1072333,"uid":136431,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:38:03.000Z","msg":"如果條友係國民黨 我會話佢算開明<br />\n但係佢係民進黨 對台灣嚟講佢分分鐘係國賊"},{"pid":"67dd32b1f22bc2bee6cccebfd5c9e8ed79f970be","tid":1072333,"uid":136431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:41:07.000Z","msg":"就算係華獨 都要修憲變第二共和確立民國在台灣啦<br />\n咩叫已經獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3e696e76572cba58b76e1c2fcb4364ddf6df0d","tid":1072333,"uid":147047,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"其實台灣一直都係國家"},{"pid":"ca362919601ae0f9f1dafce7e7cf597c1d9b9b37","tid":1072333,"uid":179775,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不嬲都要咁<br />\n<br />\n本身都獨立,又咩台獨<br />\n<br />\n唔通日本就日獨  中國就中獨"},{"pid":"cbaaad650c29f8e1507006ec7af46e3237ede04d","tid":1072333,"uid":55913,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"頭幾個回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾隻五毛趕住食屎咁衝入嚟"},{"pid":"084a2d580aaa4bc6878ea35dcf34dbc032f22970","tid":1072333,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"一面倒正評個班係咪無睇內文就打丁"},{"pid":"06878ab0a4f26c95d82f4159907753dca5a687d4","tid":1072333,"uid":136431,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"話台灣已經獨立同話香港兩制現況運作良好有咩分別"},{"pid":"e93705c50a6317a47b572180833780caa70483a6","tid":1072333,"uid":66242,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"主權國家的要件 <br />\n<br />\n根據1933年《蒙特維多國家權利義務公約》，國家做為國際法人應具備下列資格：<br />\n<br />\n固定的居民<br />\n一定界限的領土<br />\n有效的政府<br />\n與他國交往的能力"},{"pid":"12d15acef14c9e2eb0c23886cb83e9126531441b","tid":1072333,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfcba2b2f5013fea11ef6a8c5aa0ef0d765c42ff","tid":1072333,"uid":87515,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"港主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d4cd1fc64b66e6174c2aa3620fed2edb10111c","tid":1072333,"uid":61271,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"得柯文哲講野最有見解<br />\n你唔搞好經濟唔強大，你嗌咩台獨都唔會有人理你"},{"pid":"4b6128165fea85572a313a2cf9013b317535653a","tid":1072333,"uid":117679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"2f8ae1c5d5022a8aa404f64f1b97a5d38f0e878d","tid":1072333,"uid":109462,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"照佢咁講即係台獨運動已經完滿成功，各個台獨政團同組織都可以就地解散返屋企瞓覺，往後不必再提「台獨」二字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"佢嘅意思想分割「台灣」同「大陸」關係。<br />\n<br />\n台灣過去咁多年俾國際矮化，係因為國民黨死都認為有機會「反攻」大陸，拎返執政地位。所以國際間都認為台灣係「中國內政問題」。<br />\n<br />\n但民進黨就擺明台灣係一個獨立地區，所有政治、軍事都係同大陸唔同，事實上，兩者係可以完全冇關連。"},{"pid":"a0535389e0574a857ef62b00b76a61ed3518e397","tid":1072333,"uid":61660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b6128165fea85572a313a2cf9013b317535653a","tid":1072333,"uid":117679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"2f8ae1c5d5022a8aa404f64f1b97a5d38f0e878d","ti